{
  "stem": "2074.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Nazi leaders--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, in case I forget.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That woman that was hiding me-- you'll have to look at that film-- that we went back to see, her father was a big Nazi leader and his daughter was hiding me afterwards.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the beginning when I ran away, I didn't tell you-- I got carried away-- how I ran out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's another big story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you have time to listen how I ran out of that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I was working in the sewing shop, right, we knew the day that they come to take us all out from over there, not to fight us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I decided not to go, not to wait for them to come and get me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So where we had our sewing shop was outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then across the roof were living non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I crossed towards not the roof, but the attic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I crawled through the attic and I went on the other side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the people usually had their toilet in that-- it was like a barn, you know, attached to the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were keeping some-- I don't know how you'll call it-- special room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people lived in the front, and this was in the back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in there was their toilet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I ran away and, without shoes, quietly ran across.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I were standing there in their toilet while they came to take the other people from the sewing shop to be-- they searched the sewing shop.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them, they got them from the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So little did I know that the farmer walked by, and I was barefooted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the door had some kind of-- that much to see through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The farmer spotted my bare feet.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
